The next truck dumps its load a little further along the road and the truck after that dumps its load further again and so on.

The distances between the dumped loads are all equal.

The first truck makes a round trip of 600 metres and the fifth truck travels a total
of 800 metres.

III. Anyone over 18 years of age is entitled to attend the Black Rock concert.
